videos.description: Texas Tech starts off on an 11-0 run against No. 4 Baylor.
videos.headline: Upset-minded Red Raiders start game on an 11-0 run

videos.description: Justin Gray throws down a huge dunk off a Keenan Evans missed floater.
videos.headline: Gray throws down huge put back slam

videos.description: After missing a 3-point shot King McClure gets the floater to drop through the foul
videos.headline: McClure gets the floater and the foul to start the second half

videos.description: Zach Smith knocks down the three point jumper off the assist by Keenan Evans.
videos.headline: Texas Tech using 3-point shooting to keep pace with No. 4 Baylor

videos.description: Aaron Ross and Keenan Evans came up with huge baskets to fuel a 9-0 Texas Tech run against No. 4 Baylor
videos.headline: 9-0 run late in the second half has Red Raiders looking for upset over No. 4 Baylor

videos.description: Texas Tech fans storm the court after the Red Raiders upset No. 4 Baylor 82-75
videos.headline: Red Raider fans storm the court after upsetting No. 4 Baylor
